attributes.name: Nb Subscriptions
attributes.query:
select count(*) as value from customers_subscriptions
where customer_id = ?

attributes.name: #Transactions
attributes.query:
select count(*) as value
from transactions
where emitter_customer_id = ?

attributes.name: Transactions
attributes.query:
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('month', transactions.created_at) AS key, SUM(transactions.amount) / 100 AS value
from transactions 
WHERE emitter_customer_id = ?
GROUP BY key;

attributes.name: Total Spent
attributes.query:
select sum(amount + fee_amount + vat_amount) as value
from transactions
where emitter_customer_id = ?

attributes.name: Transactions
Top 10 customers by revenus
attributes.query:
SELECT customers.firstname || ' ' || customers.lastname AS key, SUM(transactions.amount) AS value
FROM transactions
JOIN customers ON transactions.emitter_customer_id = customers.id
GROUP BY key
ORDER BY value DESC
LIMIT 10;
